BootstrapLabelBlockBundle
-------------------------

Implements an AlphaLemon CMS app-block capable to manage a Twitter Bootstrap label and badges
by a nice ajax powered inteface.

[![Build Status](https://secure.travis-ci.org/alphalemon/BootstrapLabelBlockBundle.png)](http://travis-ci.org/alphalemon/BootstrapLabelBlockBundle)

Installation
------------

You can add the **BootstrapLabelBlock Bundle** to your application adding it to your composer.json
file:

.. code-block:: text

    {
        "require": {
            "alphalemon/app-bootstrap-label-bundle": "1.0.*"
        }
    }

Unit test
---------

The bunde is fully unit tested.